not moved by the plague. I'm not moved

00:42:55.920 --> 00:42:57.750
by all these things, because a plague is

00:42:57.760 --> 00:42:59.750
coming.

00:42:59.760 --> 00:43:02.790
And the Lord said, 'You must take your

00:43:02.800 --> 00:43:05.270
prayer times more seriously, and pray for

00:43:05.280 --> 00:43:07.270
these people, and get them prepared

00:43:07.280 --> 00:43:10.150
for what's coming, that you stand as a

00:43:10.160 --> 00:43:12.470
watchman on the wall and warn them, that

00:43:12.480 --> 00:43:14.309
they learn to take communion and

00:43:14.319 --> 00:43:16.470
understand who they are.'Remember what I

00:43:16.480 --> 00:43:18.790
told you. If you do not understand

00:43:18.790 --> 00:43:18.800
Psalm

00:43:18.800 --> 00:43:21.990
91, if you do not understand and

00:43:22.000 --> 00:43:24.470
have a revelation of Psalm 23 in the

00:43:24.480 --> 00:43:26.309
days ahead, you are not going to make

00:43:26.319 --> 00:43:31.270
it.

00:43:31.280 --> 00:43:34.550
You must understand who you are.

00:43:34.560 --> 00:43:36.790
You must understand the power of the

00:43:36.800 --> 00:43:39.270
covenant of what this

00:43:39.270 --> 00:43:39.280
represents—that

00:43:39.280 --> 00:43:42.309
it's not just a cup of

00:43:42.319 --> 00:43:45.510
juice and a wafer, a little cup

00:43:45.510 --> 00:43:45.520
and

00:43:45.520 --> 00:43:50.630
wafer. This represents something;

00:43:50.640 --> 00:43:54.790
it's relationship.

00:43:54.800 --> 00:43:57.750
Jesus Christ paid the price for you to

00:43:57.760 --> 00:43:59.510
walk in healing and wholeness and

00:43:59.520 --> 00:44:01.990
wellness in your life. Jesus Christ

00:44:02.000 --> 00:44:04.550
became sickness and disease; He became

00:44:04.560 --> 00:44:06.790
poor so that you might be rich through His

00:44:06.800 --> 00:44:08.630
poverty—not

00:44:08.640 --> 00:44:11.349
just monetarily,

00:44:11.359 --> 00:44:13.190
but

00:44:13.200 --> 00:44:15.589
spirit, soul, and body. Beloved, I wish

00:44:15.599 --> 00:44:19.030
above all things that you prosper and be

00:44:19.040 --> 00:44:22.069
in health, even as your soul prospers.

00:44:22.079 --> 00:44:24.710
And I even told somebody recently, 'If

00:44:24.720 --> 00:44:27.030
you're not prosperous in your soul,

00:44:27.040 --> 00:44:28.630
you're not going to be prosperous in

00:44:28.640 --> 00:44:32.069
your health all the

00:44:32.069 --> 00:44:32.079
time.'You've

00:44:32.079 --> 00:44:33.829
got to renew your mind, your

00:44:33.839 --> 00:44:36.710
will, and your emotions to the word of

00:44:36.720 --> 00:44:40.950
God, because if you do not, the

00:44:40.950 --> 00:44:40.960
devourer

00:44:40.960 --> 00:44:43.190
is at your door.

00:44:43.200 --> 00:44:45.030
And I have to do exactly what I'm

00:44:45.040 --> 00:44:46.630
preaching to you tonight all the time,

00:44:46.640 --> 00:44:49.030
too. Brandon's not an exception. Well,

00:44:49.040 --> 00:44:51.829
you know, no, seriously, the Lord told

00:44:51.839 --> 00:44:53.670
me, He said, 'You know what you sound

00:44:53.680 --> 00:44:55.349
like

00:44:55.349 --> 00:44:55.359
tonight?'And

00:44:55.359 --> 00:44:56.950
I was whining about everything that

00:44:56.960 --> 00:44:58.950
I went through last week. He said, 'You

00:44:58.960 --> 00:45:00.470
sound like Elijah over there crying at

00:45:00.480 --> 00:45:02.550
the cave.'You know, 'Oh,

00:45:02.560 --> 00:45:04.390
everything's so bad. Jezebel's after

00:45:04.400 --> 00:45:06.790
me.'But

00:45:06.800 --> 00:45:08.150
He said, 'You haven't gone to the

00:45:08.160 --> 00:45:10.390
point of saying that you just want Me to

00:45:10.400 --> 00:45:13.349
take you home like he

00:45:13.349 --> 00:45:13.359
did.'He

00:45:13.359 --> 00:45:16.309
said, 'But Brandon, what you say out

00:45:16.319 --> 00:45:19.270
of your mouth is important.

00:45:19.280 --> 00:45:21.109
What you say out of your mouth is

00:45:21.119 --> 00:45:24.150
important, for life and death is in the

00:45:24.160 --> 00:45:26.470
power of your tongue, son. All that

00:45:26.470 --> 00:45:26.480
mealy-mouthed

00:45:26.480 --> 00:45:27.910
and all that stuff you're

00:45:27.920 --> 00:45:29.270
saying right now, watch what you're

00:45:29.280 --> 00:45:31.109
saying.'He

00:45:31.119 --> 00:45:32.870
said, 'I want to open your eyes to

00:45:32.880 --> 00:45:34.790
something.'And

00:45:34.800 --> 00:45:37.030
as I was interceding and feeling

00:45:37.040 --> 00:45:38.950
sorry for myself for the week that I

00:45:38.960 --> 00:45:41.829
had, He said, 'Give your angels

00:45:41.839 --> 00:45:43.910
something to work with right now, and I

00:45:43.920 --> 00:45:45.829
want to

00:45:45.839 --> 00:45:49.430
show you.'And I saw them fighting in

00:45:49.440 --> 00:45:51.589
the spirit realm, and I saw they had

00:45:51.599 --> 00:45:53.750
Captain America shields. These angels

00:45:53.760 --> 00:45:55.349
were fighting and they had Captain

00:45:55.359 --> 00:45:58.630
America shields—the round

00:45:58.630 --> 00:45:58.640
ones—and

00:45:58.640 --> 00:45:59.990
they had swords, and they were up

00:46:00.000 --> 00:46:01.589
there battling. And He said,

00:46:01.599 --> 00:46:05.190
'Give them something to work with in the

00:46:05.200 --> 00:46:06.950
spirit realm.'And I said, 'Well, how do

00:46:06.960 --> 00:46:08.550
I do that?'He said, 'Quote the

00:46:08.560 --> 00:46:10.790
scripture concerning what you're going

00:46:10.800 --> 00:46:13.990
through. Quote the scripture.

00:46:14.000 --> 00:46:18.069
Use the sword of the Spirit.

00:46:18.079 --> 00:46:21.270
Quote the fiery word out of your mouth.

00:46:21.280 --> 00:46:22.950
Be a believing believer and not a

00:46:22.960 --> 00:46:25.990
doubter. You're an overcomer by the

00:46:26.000 --> 00:46:27.829
blood of the Lamb and by the word of

00:46:27.839 --> 00:46:30.150
your testimony.'Do you understand?

00:46:30.160 --> 00:46:32.390
You're not moved by what you see. You're

00:46:32.400 --> 00:46:34.630
not moved by what you feel. You're moved

00:46:34.640 --> 00:46:37.270
by what the word says.

00:46:37.280 --> 00:46:40.870
Now stand up and be who I've called you

00:46:40.880 --> 00:46:42.710
to be.

00:46:42.720 --> 00:46:45.109
You can either be mealy-mouthed,

00:46:45.109 --> 00:46:45.119
limp-wristed,

00:46:45.119 --> 00:46:47.349
and feel sorry for

00:46:47.359 --> 00:46:51.510
yourself, or you can be bold as a lion

00:46:51.520 --> 00:46:56.069
and say, "Thus far, Satan, and no

00:46:56.069 --> 00:46:56.079
further."It

00:46:56.079 --> 00:47:01.510
is written. It is written,

00:47:01.520 --> 00:47:04.470
"Greater is he that is in me than he that

00:47:04.480 --> 00:47:08.309
is in the world."It is written, "A

00:47:08.319 --> 00:47:10.950
thousand shall fall at my side and

00:47:10.960 --> 00:47:13.510
10,000 at my right hand, but nothing

00:47:13.520 --> 00:47:20.710
shall come nigh

00:47:20.710 --> 00:47:20.720
me."That's

00:47:20.720 --> 00:47:23.190
where you have to stand. And

00:47:23.200 --> 00:47:25.589
when the Lord showed me that, I felt

00:47:25.599 --> 00:47:27.750
when I started, I told Diana, I said,

00:47:27.760 --> 00:47:30.390
"Babe, go get that book that lady gave

00:47:30.400 --> 00:47:32.390
us,

00:47:32.400 --> 00:47:34.950
and quote those scriptures

00:47:34.960 --> 00:47:39.510
until we feel

00:47:39.510 --> 00:47:39.520
better."She

00:47:39.520 --> 00:47:40.710
goes, "How many times are we going to

00:47:40.720 --> 00:47:42.069
read them?"I said, "Until we feel

00:47:42.079 --> 00:47:45.829
better."The

00:47:45.839 --> 00:47:51.510
word will work if you work it.

00:47:51.520 --> 00:47:53.510
I said, "It don't matter how many times,

00:47:53.520 --> 00:47:56.069
hun. Even until we get tired.

00:47:56.079 --> 00:47:58.630
We quote these scriptures until they

00:47:58.640 --> 00:48:02.630
become real to

00:48:02.630 --> 00:48:02.640
us."It

00:48:02.640 --> 00:48:04.630
becomes a Rhema word on the inside of

00:48:04.640 --> 00:48:07.190
you that is not just "Twinkle, Twinkle,

00:48:07.200 --> 00:48:10.550
Little Star."It's not "how I wonder what

00:48:10.560 --> 00:48:13.030
you

00:48:13.030 --> 00:48:13.040
are,"because

00:48:13.040 --> 00:48:14.630
that's what a lot of it is when

00:48:14.640 --> 00:48:16.230
you just read something for the first

00:48:16.240 --> 00:48:18.470
time. But when it becomes Rhema to

00:48:18.470 --> 00:48:18.480
you is when

00:48:18.480 --> 00:48:21.030
it becomes real

00:48:21.040 --> 00:48:23.910
to you and has gone down so deep inside

00:48:23.920 --> 00:48:26.150
of you that there's no devil in hell

00:48:26.160 --> 00:48:27.910
that can talk you out of what he said he

00:48:27.920 --> 00:48:32.309
would do for you.

00:48:32.319 --> 00:48:34.790
There's no devil in hell that can try to

00:48:34.800 --> 00:48:36.870
convince you that you're not saved. Is

00:48:36.880 --> 00:48:38.950
that right? Some of you would fight it

00:48:38.960 --> 00:48:41.349
with all your heart.

00:48:41.359 --> 00:48:43.270
That devil tells you you're not saved.

00:48:43.280 --> 00:48:46.230
"Oh, I know I'm saved.

00:48:46.240 --> 00:48:49.109
How dare you? I'm born again by the

00:48:49.119 --> 00:48:51.750
blood of Jesus Christ. I'm born again.

00:48:51.760 --> 00:48:53.349
My name's written in the Lamb's

00:48:53.359 --> 00:48:55.910
Book of Life. Get out of here, devil. I

00:48:55.920 --> 00:48:58.230
know I'm

00:48:58.230 --> 00:48:58.240
saved."But

00:48:58.240 --> 00:49:00.870
when he comes and tells you

00:49:00.880 --> 00:49:03.430
your son's not going to make it, your

00:49:03.440 --> 00:49:05.910
son's going to serve the devil, he has a

00:49:05.910 --> 00:49:05.920
plan—the

00:49:05.920 --> 00:49:07.990
devil has a plan for your son.

00:49:08.000 --> 00:49:10.870
"Oh, the devil's going to take your son.

00:49:10.880 --> 00:49:12.069
He's going to do witchcraft. He's going

00:49:12.079 --> 00:49:14.230
to do all..."The devil's got a plan for

00:49:14.240 --> 00:49:16.549
your son.

00:49:16.559 --> 00:49:19.750
You believe it because you don't realize

00:49:19.760 --> 00:49:22.710
that he said, "Train up a child in

00:49:22.710 --> 00:49:22.720
the way

00:49:22.720 --> 00:49:24.870
they should go, and when they get older,

00:49:24.880 --> 00:49:29.349
they'll not depart from

00:49:29.359 --> 00:49:30.870
it."Regardless

00:49:30.880 --> 00:49:33.270
of how Johnny or whoever is acting right

00:49:33.280 --> 00:49:37.270
now, my God said that my children will

00:49:37.280 --> 00:49:39.670
be my offspring.

00:49:39.670 --> 00:49:39.680
The

00:49:39.680 --> 00:49:41.910
fruit of my offspring, the fruit of my

00:49:41.920 --> 00:49:44.470
children will be blessed. They're going

00:49:44.480 --> 00:49:46.309
to be blessed.

00:49:46.319 --> 00:49:47.750
They're going to be blessed coming in.

00:49:47.760 --> 00:49:49.349
They're going to be blessed coming out.

00:49:49.359 --> 00:49:53.190
My children will serve God. My children

00:49:53.200 --> 00:49:56.390
will be on fire for God.

00:49:56.400 --> 00:50:02.230
My children will not go to hell.

00:50:02.240 --> 00:50:04.470
And that's where you have to stand. Even

00:50:04.470 --> 00:50:04.480
when

00:50:04.480 --> 00:50:06.630
those kids are acting really

00:50:06.640 --> 00:50:09.270
bad,

00:50:09.280 --> 00:50:11.109
I'm training my child up in the way they

00:50:11.119 --> 00:50:14.390
should go. My kids know about Jesus. The

00:50:14.400 --> 00:50:16.630
seed of righteousness is inside of them,

00:50:16.640 --> 00:50:18.390
even if they're not displaying it right

00:50:18.400 --> 00:50:21.190
now. Now, I anoint them with oil. I

00:50:21.200 --> 00:50:23.349
anoint where they sleep. They may act rebellious

00:50:23.349 --> 00:50:23.359
in

00:50:23.359 --> 00:50:24.870
who they're hanging out

00:50:24.880 --> 00:50:27.670
with, and I might need to take a rod and

00:50:27.680 --> 00:50:30.069
spank their heinie a little bit because

00:50:30.079 --> 00:50:32.549
the Bible said if you spare the rod,

00:50:32.559 --> 00:50:35.109
you spoil the child. And it's not abuse;

00:50:35.119 --> 00:50:38.069
it's love.

00:50:38.079 --> 00:50:39.829
But either way, we're going to walk in

00:50:39.839 --> 00:50:44.150
love up in here. And love corrects.

00:50:44.160 --> 00:50:47.750
Love disciplines,

00:50:47.760 --> 00:50:50.069
not abuse. It didn't say beat them when

00:50:50.079 --> 00:50:51.589
you're angry.

00:50:51.599 --> 00:50:53.670
That's wrong.

00:50:53.680 --> 00:50:55.750
It's like I heard Kim Clement say, "If

