00:51:09.680 --> 00:51:12.069
going to be real with y'all. God's not

00:51:12.079 --> 00:51:14.470
angry.

00:51:14.480 --> 00:51:17.030
God's not up there always conspiring

00:51:17.040 --> 00:51:19.430
