00:51:19.440 --> 00:51:21.670
"What is he doing today, Jesus? I think

00:51:21.680 --> 00:51:23.190
I'll slap him in the head with

00:51:23.200 --> 00:51:25.589
something."I

00:51:25.599 --> 00:51:29.670
realize that God is a God of love.

00:51:29.680 --> 00:51:31.829
God is not conspiring up there thinking

00:51:31.839 --> 00:51:33.109
how he's going to make your life

00:51:33.119 --> 00:51:36.069
miserable. "Beloved, I wish above all

00:51:36.079 --> 00:51:39.750
things that you prosper and be in health,

00:51:39.760 --> 00:51:43.190
even as your soul prospers."Above all

00:51:43.200 --> 00:51:45.430
things,

00:51:45.440 --> 00:51:47.750
everything

00:51:47.760 --> 00:51:51.030
for you to have a good and expected end.

00:51:51.040 --> 00:51:54.710
That's a good God.

00:51:54.720 --> 00:51:56.470
But most people think God's up there

00:51:56.480 --> 00:51:58.150
mad,

00:51:58.160 --> 00:52:01.510
