00:52:01.520 --> 00:52:04.790
at Israel, he's mad at

00:52:04.800 --> 00:52:07.510
Thailand, he's mad at China, he's mad...

00:52:07.520 --> 00:52:12.309
No, God's not mad.

00:52:12.319 --> 00:52:14.230
Now,

00:52:14.240 --> 00:52:16.390
what does the Bible say? Seedtime and

00:52:16.400 --> 00:52:18.710
