daughters and your sons saved, to have

00:55:01.040 --> 00:55:03.829
revival in your homes, for husbands and

00:55:03.839 --> 00:55:08.230
wives to come together with great...

00:55:08.240 --> 00:55:09.510
"You know what, devil? We're going to

00:55:09.520 --> 00:55:11.349
punch you in the head today as a

00:55:11.359 --> 00:55:13.990
unit. We're going to be more in love.

00:55:14.000 --> 00:55:15.670
We're going to walk in love. We're going

00:55:15.680 --> 00:55:17.430
to have more friendship up in here.

00:55:17.440 --> 00:55:19.270
We're going to pray together. We're

00:55:19.280 --> 00:55:21.190
going to read the Bible together. And

00:55:21.200 --> 00:55:22.630
we're going to be more of a unit

00:55:22.640 --> 00:55:24.950
together than ever before. And we're not

00:55:24.960 --> 00:55:26.950
going to allow the devil to come in and

00:55:26.960 --> 00:55:29.430
rob our marriage through strife, through

00:55:29.440 --> 00:55:32.309
bitterness, through

00:55:32.309 --> 00:55:32.319
whatever."The

00:55:32.319 --> 00:55:34.390
Lord told me, he said, "As the days

00:55:34.400 --> 00:55:36.630
approach, Brandon, you must make sure

00:55:36.640 --> 00:55:40.069
strife, if it ever exists, as a

00:55:40.079 --> 00:55:41.750
minimum, do not allow it in your home

00:55:41.760 --> 00:55:45.670
ever. Always diffuse it at all cost.

00:55:45.680 --> 00:55:48.870
It's not worth it. Make sure love is a

00:55:52.799 --> 00:55:56.069
pillar in your home.

00:55:56.079 --> 00:56:00.390
Do not allow strife in at all costs.

00:56:00.400 --> 00:56:06.390
It's not worth

00:56:06.390 --> 00:56:06.400
it."So

00:56:06.400 --> 00:56:10.470
hopefully this helps you tonight.

00:56:10.480 --> 00:56:11.829
It's just stuff that we're dealing with,

00:56:11.839 --> 00:56:13.829
and that's what Diana and I talk

00:56:13.839 --> 00:56:15.349
about.

00:56:15.359 --> 00:56:22.069
It's what prepares us

00:56:22.079 --> 00:56:24.069
to make sure that we're walking in, and

00:56:24.079 --> 00:56:28.309
we have our t's crossed and our i's

00:56:28.309 --> 00:56:28.319
doted,

00:56:28.319 --> 00:56:30.870
and you're ready,

00:56:30.880 --> 00:56:33.109
and you have your eyes peeled.

00:56:33.119 --> 00:56:35.190
It's like talking to people, and they

00:56:35.200 --> 00:56:37.190
say, "I watch the crowd. I watch

00:56:37.190 --> 00:56:37.200
this."Yes,

00:56:37.200 --> 00:56:39.030
I'm a people watcher, too. I

00:56:39.040 --> 00:56:40.870
hear them. I never let my

00:56:40.880 --> 00:56:43.030
guard down. Yes, I know. But

00:56:43.030 --> 00:56:43.040
we've

00:56:43.040 --> 00:56:44.789
got to have times of infilling and

00:56:44.799 --> 00:56:47.910
refreshing, too. We must have a time to

00:56:47.920 --> 00:56:50.710
drink from the Father and to make sure

00:56:50.720 --> 00:56:53.510
our cup is full of oil,

00:56:53.520 --> 00:56:55.910
our lamps are full, our lives are

00:56:55.920 --> 00:56:58.549
full and ready so that the enemy is

00:56:58.559 --> 00:57:01.829
not able to come and eat our lunch.

00:57:01.839 --> 00:57:03.990
He looks for the weak ones that are

00:57:04.000 --> 00:57:06.710
separated from the fold. The wolf does.

00:57:06.720 --> 00:57:09.030
Remember, the wolf is looking for the

00:57:09.040 --> 00:57:12.309
weak and sick ones.

00:57:12.319 --> 00:57:14.309
He doesn't go after the strong ones that

00:57:14.319 --> 00:57:16.549
have the full meat and

00:57:16.549 --> 00:57:16.559
are

00:57:16.559 --> 00:57:18.549
ready to fight. He looks for the ones

00:57:18.559 --> 00:57:20.390
that look like they're

00:57:20.390 --> 00:57:20.400
malnourished

00:57:20.400 --> 00:57:23.270
and off to the side of the fold.

00:57:23.280 --> 00:57:25.750
'Can I take him out?

00:57:25.760 --> 00:57:28.870
Can I take you

00:57:28.870 --> 00:57:28.880
out?'Does

00:57:28.880 --> 00:57:31.670
that make sense? You don't go after

00:57:31.680 --> 00:57:33.510
the strong ones; you go after the weak

00:57:33.520 --> 00:57:38.630
ones.

00:57:38.640 --> 00:57:42.309
So I want you to remain strong.

00:57:42.319 --> 00:57:44.870
I want you to remain strong and make

00:57:44.880 --> 00:57:48.069
this your best

00:57:48.069 --> 00:57:48.079
friend—the

00:57:48.079 --> 00:57:50.870
word of God in these last days. I

00:57:50.880 --> 00:57:52.710
even told certain folks

00:57:52.720 --> 00:57:56.870
I talked to, 'You must read Psalms 91 and

00:57:56.880 --> 00:58:00.789
Psalms 23 more and more and

00:58:00.789 --> 00:58:00.799
more.'You

00:58:00.799 --> 00:58:03.910
must know this. You must understand the

00:58:03.920 --> 00:58:06.789
power of communion.

00:58:06.799 --> 00:58:09.349
You must understand this:

00:58:09.359 --> 00:58:13.270
the meal that heals.

00:58:13.280 --> 00:58:16.309
It's so important, ladies and gentlemen.

00:58:16.319 --> 00:58:19.030
It's so important.

00:58:19.040 --> 00:58:21.109
I tell you this, and it's like I say all

00:58:21.119 --> 00:58:23.510
the time, if what you're doing is not

00:58:23.520 --> 00:58:26.470
working and you keep going down the same

00:58:26.480 --> 00:58:29.190
road all the time expecting different

00:58:29.200 --> 00:58:32.390
results, it's insanity.

00:58:32.400 --> 00:58:35.030
Try something new. That's why

00:58:35.030 --> 00:58:35.040
Diana

00:58:35.040 --> 00:58:37.030
and I, when we come to Megan and we do

00:58:37.040 --> 00:58:39.670
the therapies for Megan, if we didn't

00:58:39.680 --> 00:58:42.630
see results within the first 100

00:58:42.640 --> 00:58:45.829
days because our budgets were limited,

00:58:45.839 --> 00:58:48.630
you don't keep doing the same thing

00:58:48.640 --> 00:58:51.349
expecting different results. After a

00:58:51.359 --> 00:58:53.829
point of time, you realize this isn't

00:58:53.839 --> 00:58:56.309
bearing any fruit.

00:58:56.319 --> 00:58:59.990
It's time to change directions.

00:59:00.000 --> 00:59:02.230
So if you don't have different fruit in

00:59:02.240 --> 00:59:05.270
your life after a while, and you don't

00:59:05.280 --> 00:59:07.030
see first the blade, then the ear, then

00:59:07.040 --> 00:59:09.430
the full manifestation—even a little bit

00:59:09.440 --> 00:59:11.829
of change with even coming and praying

00:59:11.839 --> 00:59:16.549
with me—then do something different.

00:59:16.559 --> 00:59:18.789
I do not want to be something that is a

00:59:18.799 --> 00:59:21.109
stumbling block for anybody.

00:59:21.119 --> 00:59:23.670
If you don't see change from praying with

00:59:23.680 --> 00:59:25.829
me and the things that I'm telling you,

00:59:25.839 --> 00:59:27.750
and it's not causing you to

00:59:27.760 --> 00:59:30.710
grow from glory to glory, then find

00:59:30.720 --> 00:59:35.510
something that does.

00:59:35.520 --> 00:59:37.910
Then find something that does, because we

00:59:37.920 --> 00:59:43.750
have to change from glory to glory.

00:59:43.760 --> 00:59:47.349
The word must change you from the inside

00:59:47.359 --> 00:59:50.230
out. If it is not, you're becoming

00:59:50.240 --> 00:59:53.510
stagnant and the enemy will devour you,

00:59:53.520 --> 00:59:55.430
especially with what I've seen coming.

00:59:55.440 --> 00:59:58.230
You must hear me.

00:59:58.240 --> 01:00:00.069
The Lord said, 'Remember, I was driving

01:00:00.069 --> 01:00:00.079
down...'I'll

01:00:00.079 --> 01:00:02.069
tell you where I was. I was

01:00:02.069 --> 01:00:02.079
on

01:00:02.079 --> 01:00:03.670
I-35

01:00:03.680 --> 01:00:08.069
and Covell Road in Edmond, Oklahoma. You

01:00:08.079 --> 01:00:10.230
can look it up—I-35

01:00:10.230 --> 01:00:10.240
and Covell

01:00:10.240 --> 01:00:13.349
Road. And there's a

01:00:13.359 --> 01:00:17.109
Starbucks there and a Braum's there.

01:00:17.119 --> 01:00:18.870
And there's a field over here with a

01:00:18.880 --> 01:00:21.910
Showtime Cinema Theater. I exited off

01:00:21.920 --> 01:00:24.069
that road.

01:00:24.079 --> 01:00:26.309
I took a right and I was going

01:00:26.319 --> 01:00:29.190
down the road to go to the

01:00:29.200 --> 01:00:31.349
post office.

01:00:31.359 --> 01:00:33.750
And the Lord spoke to me when I got off

01:00:33.760 --> 01:00:35.990
that road that day, and he said to me,

01:00:36.000 --> 01:00:38.470
'Brandon,

01:00:38.480 --> 01:00:42.470
very sobering days are coming.

01:00:42.480 --> 01:00:45.270
Very sobering days are coming to the

01:00:45.280 --> 01:00:48.069
church. Sobering days are coming to the

01:00:48.079 --> 01:00:49.829
world.'And

01:00:49.839 --> 01:00:51.750
he said, 'But what's the opposite of

01:00:51.760 --> 01:00:53.430
sober?'And

01:00:53.440 --> 01:00:58.470
I said, 'Lord, drunk

01:00:58.470 --> 01:00:58.480
is.'And

01:00:58.480 --> 01:01:02.150
he said, 'Yes. Be being filled

01:01:02.160 --> 01:01:04.549
with the Holy Spirit to overflowing like

01:01:04.559 --> 01:01:06.069
a bubbling, bubbling, bubbling,

01:01:06.079 --> 01:01:08.710
bubbling. Let it be bubbling up out of

01:01:08.720 --> 01:01:10.950
you like a river of water coming up out

01:01:10.960 --> 01:01:13.270
of you by drinking of my spirit every

01:01:13.280 --> 01:01:16.710
day. Be being filled with the spirit

01:01:16.720 --> 01:01:18.870
every day. Brandon,

01:01:18.880 --> 01:01:21.109
don't get dry.

01:01:21.119 --> 01:01:23.750
Drink, Brandon.

01:01:23.760 --> 01:01:26.069
Be drunk in my spirit. Be filled with my

01:01:26.079 --> 01:01:27.589
spirit,

01:01:27.599 --> 01:01:30.710
for sobering days are

01:01:30.710 --> 01:01:30.720
coming.'And

01:01:30.720 --> 01:01:33.109
he said, 'Do you remember the scene

01:01:33.119 --> 01:01:36.710
in Mary Poppins, "I Love to

01:01:36.710 --> 01:01:36.720
Laugh,"where

01:01:36.720 --> 01:01:39.589
Dick Van Dyke was floating on the

01:01:39.599 --> 01:01:40.950
ceiling? They were laughing and they

01:01:40.960 --> 01:01:44.069
were just having a good

01:01:44.069 --> 01:01:44.079
time.'He

01:01:44.079 --> 01:01:46.630
said they were laughing.

01:01:46.640 --> 01:01:49.910
He said, 'Learn to laugh more.

01:01:49.920 --> 01:01:52.870
Learn to laugh more. You're gonna have

01:01:52.880 --> 01:01:56.150
to learn how to laugh and have fun in

01:01:56.160 --> 01:01:58.950
life with the sobering times that are

01:01:58.960 --> 01:02:00.549
coming.

01:02:00.559 --> 01:02:03.430
Don't allow the things I show you

01:02:03.440 --> 01:02:05.750
prophetically to get down on the inside

01:02:05.760 --> 01:02:07.670
of you to the point where it changes

01:02:07.680 --> 01:02:10.549
you. You get filled with my spirit and

01:02:10.559 --> 01:02:13.510
pray out of the spirit,

01:02:13.520 --> 01:02:15.349
because when you see what I

01:02:15.359 --> 01:02:18.390
see,

01:02:18.400 --> 01:02:21.349
it has a tendency to get heavy.'Then some

01:02:21.359 --> 01:02:22.630
people say when I first start these

01:02:22.640 --> 01:02:25.750
streams, 'Brandon, you seem

01:02:25.760 --> 01:02:27.270
heavy.'Yeah,

01:02:27.280 --> 01:02:30.710
because I see the depth of the vision.

01:02:30.720 --> 01:02:33.510
I see things that I can't even allow myself

01:02:33.510 --> 01:02:33.520
to

01:02:33.520 --> 01:02:35.670
speak about

01:02:35.680 --> 01:02:38.789
upon this platform.

01:02:38.799 --> 01:02:42.390
There's things that you'll never know,

01:02:42.400 --> 01:02:44.309
never know,

01:02:44.319 --> 01:02:46.470
because I cannot allow that to be heard

01:02:46.480 --> 01:02:48.309
by the public

01:02:48.319 --> 01:02:51.349
because it would put people in danger.

01:02:51.359 --> 01:02:53.190
But the Lord has allowed me to say

01:02:53.200 --> 01:02:54.950
certain things to a certain individual

01:02:54.960 --> 01:02:57.270
now, and I'm thankful for

01:02:57.280 --> 01:02:58.950
that.

01:02:58.960 --> 01:03:02.230
But at the same time, the watchman gift

01:03:02.240 --> 01:03:05.030
is very heavy,

01:03:05.040 --> 01:03:06.870
some of these things. But you know what he

01:03:06.880 --> 01:03:10.069
said to combat it with? Laughter.

01:03:10.079 --> 01:03:12.470
Laughter in him. Be being filled with

01:03:12.480 --> 01:03:16.549
the spirit for what's coming. So I tell

01:03:16.559 --> 01:03:18.630
you all this so that you prepare

01:03:18.640 --> 01:03:21.029
yourself: be being filled with the

01:03:21.039 --> 01:03:23.190
spirit with laughter.

01:03:23.200 --> 01:03:26.470
Be happy, because a merry heart doeth

01:03:26.480 --> 01:03:29.109
good like a medicine, and a

01:03:29.109 --> 01:03:29.119
broken

01:03:29.119 --> 01:03:31.910
spirit

01:03:31.920 --> 01:03:33.829
dries the bones. A weary

01:03:33.839 --> 01:03:35.829
spirit dries the bones. A heavy spirit

01:03:35.839 --> 01:03:38.230
dries the bones. You need to be being

01:03:38.240 --> 01:03:41.430
filled with the Holy Spirit to the

01:03:41.440 --> 01:03:44.470
overflowing with laughter and joy in

01:03:44.480 --> 01:03:48.309
your households. How can you become

01:03:48.319 --> 01:03:50.230
happy and your wife follow you if you're

01:03:50.240 --> 01:03:52.230
always somber, like you've been

01:03:52.240 --> 01:03:56.309
eating dill pickles

01:03:56.309 --> 01:03:56.319
and

01:03:56.319 --> 01:03:58.150
you're

01:03:58.160 --> 01:04:02.309
sour, and you're going,

01:04:02.319 --> 01:04:05.109
'Yeah, I'm heavy. I'm weary. I'm carrying

01:04:05.119 --> 01:04:08.150
the load. I've got the spiritual load on

01:04:08.160 --> 01:04:11.029
me today.

01:04:11.039 --> 01:04:13.829
I've seen so

01:04:13.829 --> 01:04:13.839
much.'How—what

01:04:13.839 --> 01:04:17.990
good is that?

01:04:18.000 --> 01:04:19.670
I started learning about

01:04:19.680 --> 01:04:21.990
the spirit of foreboding, walking around

01:04:22.000 --> 01:04:24.390
making sure it's not just me hearing

01:04:24.400 --> 01:04:26.549
things and, 'Oh, the devil said there's

01:04:26.559 --> 01:04:28.470
something, I hear there's something

01:04:28.480 --> 01:04:30.309
in the spirit realm that feels heavy all

01:04:30.319 --> 01:04:35.270
the time.'I feel that heaviness. Brother,

01:04:35.280 --> 01:04:36.630
you can walk around like that and

01:04:36.630 --> 01:04:36.640
it'll

01:04:36.640 --> 01:04:40.069
choke the life right out of you

01:04:40.079 --> 01:04:41.750
to the point where it's like, 'What am I

01:04:41.760 --> 01:04:44.390
even here for?

01:04:44.400 --> 01:04:46.390
There's such a heaviness in the

01:04:46.390 --> 01:04:46.400
atmosphere.'So

01:04:46.400 --> 01:04:48.390
you've

01:04:48.400 --> 01:04:51.430
got to check that

01:04:51.440 --> 01:04:53.109
and know the difference between a spirit

01:04:53.119 --> 01:04:55.349
of

01:04:55.349 --> 01:04:55.359
foreboding.

01:04:55.359 --> 01:04:57.349
A spirit of foreboding will choke the

01:04:57.359 --> 01:04:59.910
life out of you.

01:04:59.920 --> 01:05:05.750
It will make sure you always feel heavy,

01:05:05.760 --> 01:05:07.270
versus

01:05:07.280 --> 01:05:10.230
a call to

01:05:10.230 --> 01:05:10.240
prayer—a

01:05:10.240 --> 01:05:12.150
call to prayer. There's a big

01:05:12.160 --> 01:05:13.190
difference between a spirit of

01:05:13.190 --> 01:05:13.200
foreboding

01:05:13.200 --> 01:05:17.430
and a spirit of intercession.

01:05:17.440 --> 01:05:20.150
You'll have to look it up. A spirit of

01:05:20.150 --> 01:05:20.160
foreboding

01:05:20.160 --> 01:05:22.950
is terrible. And I used to

01:05:22.960 --> 01:05:26.150
walk around with that all the

01:05:26.150 --> 01:05:26.160
time—I'm

01:05:26.160 --> 01:05:27.829
talking the first ten years of my

01:05:27.839 --> 01:05:30.390
marriage. I'm always carrying this,

01:05:30.400 --> 01:05:32.710
Diana. And she goes, 'Man, I ain't never

01:05:32.720 --> 01:05:34.630
seen nobody like that.'Intercessory

01:05:34.630 --> 01:05:34.640
prayer—and

01:05:34.640 --> 01:05:36.150
she used to say this when

01:05:36.160 --> 01:05:37.990
we were first married—'Intercessory prayer

01:05:37.990 --> 01:05:38.000
on

01:05:38.000 --> 01:05:40.870
this side of it sucks,

01:05:40.880 --> 01:05:43.750
just being real, because it's heavy,

01:05:43.760 --> 01:05:46.950
Brandon, and I don't like this.'And I

01:05:46.960 --> 01:05:49.109
said, 'Well, I'm just doing my job. I'm

01:05:49.119 --> 01:05:52.230
sorry. I'm just doing my job.

01:05:52.240 --> 01:05:54.870
I'm just carrying the world, praying for

01:05:54.880 --> 01:06:00.710
the world. Just pray. Oh God, oh God,

01:06:00.710 --> 01:06:00.720
foreboding.'And

01:06:00.720 --> 01:06:04.150
then I realized one day

01:06:04.160 --> 01:06:06.789
the Lord said, 'My burden is easy and my yoke

01:06:06.799 --> 01:06:09.589
is

01:06:09.599 --> 01:06:13.510
light, son.

01:06:13.520 --> 01:06:16.470
I want you to have fun and enjoy life

01:06:16.480 --> 01:06:19.029
and have it more abundantly.'So I'm not

01:06:19.039 --> 01:06:20.630
trying to tell you all this—what I'm trying

01:06:20.640 --> 01:06:22.789
to tell you is I'm not trying to tell

01:06:22.799 --> 01:06:25.510
you to live underneath the

01:06:25.520 --> 01:06:28.069
umbrella when it's not storming; the sky

01:06:28.079 --> 01:06:30.549
is not falling. I want you to be being

01:06:30.559 --> 01:06:32.789
filled with love and joy and enjoy your

01:06:32.799 --> 01:06:36.150
life as I bring these things to you. I

01:06:36.160 --> 01:06:38.150
know it's heavy.

01:06:38.160 --> 01:06:40.789
I know it's heavy, and what we might see

01:06:40.799 --> 01:06:43.510
tonight could be heavy.

01:06:43.520 --> 01:06:45.510
But I'm taking the time to teach you a

01:06:45.520 --> 01:06:47.430
little bit before I just jump in the

01:06:47.440 --> 01:06:50.789
river. You have to be filled with joy.

01:06:50.799 --> 01:06:53.430
You have to be filled with hope, because

01:06:53.440 --> 01:06:56.150
God is a God of hope, and God is a God of

01:06:56.160 --> 01:06:59.990
peace, and God is a God of fun.

01:07:00.000 --> 01:07:01.990
He even said, 'Hey, the fun has just

01:07:01.990 --> 01:07:02.000
begun.'And

01:07:02.000 --> 01:07:04.069
he even said that last

01:07:04.079 --> 01:07:05.990
night. He said, 'Remember I told you the

01:07:06.000 --> 01:07:08.870
fun has just begun.

01:07:08.880 --> 01:07:10.630
As you're seeing all these things that

01:07:10.640 --> 01:07:12.950
are bad and I'm warning you of these

01:07:12.960 --> 01:07:15.270
things to pray about, the fun has just

01:07:15.270 --> 01:07:15.280
begun.'He's

01:07:15.280 --> 01:07:19.910
joyful. He's happy. He's not,

01:07:19.910 --> 01:07:19.920
'Oh,

